room_title: Escape room "Da Vinci's Secret" by Escape Game Erie in Erie
room_description: The Louvre is on lockdown after a bomb threat poses real danger to the collection of the Da Vinci artifacts. Your best friend, the esteemed expert on Leonardo's work, has stepped in and deciphered the bomb's code. However, the police have detained her as a suspect! Can you and your group decipher her messages and retrace her cryptic trail to retrieve the bomb code and clear your friend's name?
